Package: ForestTools
Type: Package
Title: Analyzing Remotely Sensed Forest Data
Version: 0.1.5
Date: 2017-09-07
Author: Andrew Plowright
Maintainer: Andrew Plowright <andrew.plowright@alumni.ubc.ca>
